These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, peas, corn, lettuce
1. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | zucchini | peas | corn | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, almond-milk, cola
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk | cola | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, singing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | photography | singing | camping | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, documentary, horror, time-travel
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama | time-travel | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, skateboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | climbing | skateboarding | biathlon | tennis |

