.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, nectarine, spinach, eggplant
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating cherry and the person eating eggplant##2
3. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | eggplant | nectarine | cherry | spinach |

