.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, gospel, salsa
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | punk | d&b | salsa |

 